       its rendered height drives the container height. This keeps the
       container's bounding rect identical to the photo's bounding rect at
       ALL zoom levels (aspect-ratio + object-fit:contain accumulate sub-pixel
       letterboxing that becomes a visible vertical stretch at high zoom). */
